   keywords = {Animal Genetics and Genomics,Behavioral Sciences,Biological Techniques,Biomedicine,Neurobiology,Neurosciences,general},
   note = {One thing about control within DMFC: recently the talk has been about monitoring functions in addition to control specification. Pain and negative emotions could be signals being monitored here, and as such they would not show unique activation patterns.},
