   note = {This wasn't super relevant. It just shows that you can use single-trial EEG phase information from hippocampus, rhinal cortex, and their difference, to predict performance on a recognition experiment using SVM. <br/><br/>It could be useful to say that slow frequency phase information can has been used to predict performance as an aside, though. It also had some potentially useful references.},
